1.  Open [index.html](file:///c:/Users/Tomi/PR%C3%B3ba/index.html) in your browser.
2.  The app automatically generates realistic mock data for Czech Liga Pro players.
3.  Look for the **Green Neon Bars** indicating a high probability (>60-70%).
4.  Click the **Refresh (‚Üª)** button to generate a new set of matches and test different scenarios.

